      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Omnidirectional Threats",
        "Client": "Plainly Dressed Lady",
        "Description": "Hi, I\u0027d like to speak to whoever is in\r\ncharge here. Yes, I heard that there\r\nwere two monsters in the Lava Caverns.\r\nThis is completely unacceptable!\r\nIf something is not done about this\r\nright away, I WILL be contacting\r\nthe guild to file a complaint!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Rakna-Kadaki and a Khezu",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Des menaces partout",
        "Client": "Femme ordinaire",
        "Description": "H\u00E9, est-ce que je pourrais parler\r\n\u00E0 la personne en charge ici ? Il\r\npara\u00EEt qu\u0027il y aurait deux monstres\r\ndans les Cavernes de lave. C\u0027est\r\ninacceptable ! Si rien n\u0027est fait\r\npour rem\u00E9dier \u00E0 cela, la Guilde\r\nva m\u0027entendre, \u00E7a c\u0027est s\u00FBr !",
